01:00:59,788 --> 01:01:00,830
Karena dia Mubaek.

839
01:01:01,623 --> 01:01:05,877
Kau percaya Mubaek sepenuhnya
dan mengikutinya, tapi diserang?

840
01:01:06,211 --> 01:01:08,380
